{
 "name": "RPlog_Senate_Assembled",
 "title": "Senate Assembled",
 "summary": "Presiding over a full session of the New Republic Senate, President Leia Organa walks the assembly through a grim agenda while the newly seated Senator Dalek Rolynd looks on, wary and out of his political depth. Senator Al'Dira briefs the chamber on the growing Imperial naval threat to Chandrila near Bandomeer, and Leia announces the suspicious death of Chandrila's Senator Hastell. The Wookiee Senator Tarshyyk delivers an impassioned report on the mass abduction of his people by the Trandoshan Bloodclaw clan -- funded through a CSA-linked front company allegedly serving Imperial Lord Thel -- and lays out the choice between a surgical strike on the Bloodclaw leader or fueling a rival-clan war on Dosha. Dalek argues the Republic is honor-bound to defend its Wookiee members, and the session closes with updates on Corellia's cartel warfare and the Bothan Senator Braal Vey'la's bittersweet report on Bothawui's recovery and its thousand still-missing prisoners.",
